- **δγ (Earth/Humavita — Cycling)**: slowness|acceleration — Slowness as immune function, not inefficiency. Slow loops preserve resilience.
- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: containment|shortcut — AI as containment instrument. Never shorten latency; render structure legibly.

